25|$|Online investors {{typically}} invest {{without help}} from a trained stockbroker or investment adviser, and may not fully understand the potential risks of investing in a particular security. Inexperienced investors are easy prey for stock manipulators and pump and dump schemes often associated with <b>penny</b> <b>stocks.</b> For this reason, many online brokers offer a number of investment tools to educate and inform new investors.|$|R
